name: Absence
description: After watching movie "Parasite", I was inspired by the movie and headed out to shoot some photos, and ended up on this neighborhood which wasn't too far from my home. No space in between buildings and tight space doesn't give give much light even during daytime to people who's living in these buildings. Couldn't feel it's like a place that people live. / Format : Jpeg / Size : 6000x3750
